Package codenames

Class Game

java.lang.Object
codenames.Game
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
@Entity public class Game extends Object implements Serializable
Game object that represents one instance of a code names board game. Each individual game can be seen as a "Lobby" in certain screens.
